Synopsis: Daniel holds a secret dream of becoming a writer. In the pursuit of excitement, he finds himself trapped in an illicit affair with the wife of a powerful businessman. Things take another dramatic turn when he falls in love with the same businessman’s daughter. After his mistakes are revealed, he abandons the life set out for him and meets – Tom; a simple fisherman who helps Daniel achieve his true potential in life.  Starring: Elani Dekker, Albert Maritz, Zane Meas, Hendrik Cronje Directed by: Hendrik Cronje Rating: 13 Language and Sex     